    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 factors and determined that, taken in aggregate, the evidence supports acceptance of the CFD model for the stated COU. The late-appended experimental hemolysis validation result (post-signing) was considered informally by reviewers and noted to further support the model's predictive capability, though the package was not re-signed following its addition. Remaining factor gaps are acknowledged and accepted under a risk-informed decision framework pending supplemental testing.",
